title: DAZ3D 22902 - Natsumi for Genesis 3 Female
description:
Details

The beauty of summer comes alive in our dear Natsumi. She is a delicate doll with a milky porcelain complexion who comes complete with a full beauty kit of fresh make-up options to keep her ready for all the fun summer can bring.

The set comes complete with custom crafted High Definition Morphs, and a highly detailed texture set, suitable for Iray and 3Delight.
